snippet.title: Granado Espada V10.6 Trailer
snippet.description:
As the mysterious force sealing Lucifer Castle fades away, the ancient hinges of the castle creaks as the door slowly opens up, as if to beckon to the brave pioneers who stood without to enter. What perilous danger lies ahead, awaiting the brave pioneers who have gathered to end the reign of Montoro.

"Welcome to my castle, it will be the last place you'll ever step foot in"
